{"tid":376931,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE英文作文綜合/通識交文區","createTime":"2017-08-27T10:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T13:24:59.000Z","uid":11058,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b722f0c8b028a17dab0f26b3a68982a084e281aa","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T10:52:41.000Z","msg":"就快開學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有8個月左右就到2017DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升中六同學如果未開始溫書就快d開始喇<br />\n<br />\n如果大家作左文<br />\n又或者做左通識既題目 <br />\n又想搵人幫手改吓既 <br />\n不妨send 比我睇睇  <br />\n不論Past papers或者出版社題目都可以架 <br />\n<br />\n你可以收到comments之餘 <br />\n我又可以改多啲文增加經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會盡快幫你改好然後send翻比你 <br />\n快則一日慢則一星期  <br />\n<br />\n但代價好簡單就係比我用作教育用途    <br />\n幫下你地既師弟師妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n作好可以send去awtutorial@hotmail.com <br />\n你可以<br />\n1. send .doc比我<br />\n2. send SCAN既手寫文比我 (可以用手機dl camscanner)<br />\n(影相就唔改啦好難睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有問題都可以係到問架<br />\n<br />\n利申：做緊私補 主修英文 英文通識5** <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">如果2018DSE 2019DSE 2020DSE想學英文既話 <br />\n可以like一like我ig 同埋whatsapp我問課堂資料 <br />\n記住留意喇 <br />\nig: awtutorial_paperman</span></span>"},{"pid":"8353fc6c035f0962f266b1bdd25d9f53e558cfe4","tid":376931,"uid":27097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"可唔可以喺度問英文嘢㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18dse，諗緊補唔補英文"},{"pid":"0ddd7206bbbc10459ff3fa544c3c24d8826c589d","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以喺度問英文嘢㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n18dse，諗緊補唔補英文</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以呀<br />\n順便推下post"},{"pid":"4341962577f475768f81e9433646cae77fd1bcbc","tid":376931,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5447543cd8ad2b0d228ad5b852c2f9b9b4133f3d","tid":376931,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:35:09.000Z","msg":"support<br />\n<br />\n樓主有無tg?"},{"pid":"0e27fbd25a37f1262bee5d2bdfdd8df5e4fa6278","tid":376931,"uid":114159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:39:26.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2016搵你改文 評語中肯 作文成功升級"},{"pid":"1fababc2f1614cfcc73ad132e598c3c44a6b4ece","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>support<br />\n<br />\n樓主有無tg?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀<br />\n用左tg就冇人上黎幫手推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e00ee058a5027bbee108c3526bcb11a2f9d5245","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2016搵你改文 評語中肯 作文成功升級</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你支持呀！<br />\n果陣仲係好缺乏經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家改多左好左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8faa3cb622bfd0a4821498b09132f3cd0b782930","tid":376931,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:20:45.000Z","msg":"我想問點樣準備英文作文elective既vocab，上網google打social issue ?"},{"pid":"78ceba6a0f05baffdf49d812014248f6b3d664fe","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:24:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問點樣準備英文作文elective既vocab，上網google打social issue ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRead more, recite more, write more<br />\n我考DSE之前真係拎住本字典去背<br />\n同埋睇多D熱門既時事文章<br />\n特別係commentary<br />\n同埋記吓唔同既concept words<br />\n咁就多好多"},{"pid":"b48a95175322cd75b06470cbb95c33054a7d215c","tid":376931,"uid":114159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"習慣上網的話可用<a href=\"https://www.vocabulary.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vocabulary.com&d=%2FMd9pphgY26K6J%2BQVtP%2F6i7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=8357a5ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vocabulary.com</a>儲詞彙<br />\n溫故知新 一試難忘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ed3c59393e01f5612782ad530f006c700f7429","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T04:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ba9b83a0251bab30c6940cea86f8916b5fcc59","tid":376931,"uid":97598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:19:32.000Z","msg":"講起改文就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲學生係唔知邊度背埋啲唔係everyday English嘅expression<br />\n跟住我要查字典查用法就串我唔識<br />\n我感覺一般學生比坊間灌輸咗錯誤嘅學英文觀念。"},{"pid":"31888dabd7b46dfa48f25d95ade03010c35b3b70","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講起改文就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲學生係唔知邊度背埋啲唔係everyday English嘅expression<br />\n跟住我要查字典查用法就串我唔識<br />\n我感覺一般學生比坊間灌輸咗錯誤嘅學英文觀念。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時改左佢地D奇怪字<br />\n但佢地下篇又keep住用真係好嬲<br />\n好多所謂名師亂咁教D字搞到大家以為自己英文水平好好<br />\n但其實用落d context好奇怪"},{"pid":"1756cb9e48cebb3796c364ecd59703c6745c448e","tid":376931,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問點樣準備英文作文elective既vocab，上網google打social issue ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRead more, recite more, write more<br />\n我考DSE之前真係拎住本字典去背<br />\n同埋睇多D熱門既時事文章<br />\n特別係commentary<br />\n同埋記吓唔同既concept words<br />\n咁就多好多</blockquote><br />\n咩concept words"},{"pid":"03583d09a0d57d839272f4ed8ec245931c6145bf","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T09:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問點樣準備英文作文elective既vocab，上網google打social issue ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRead more, recite more, write more<br />\n我考DSE之前真係拎住本字典去背<br />\n同埋睇多D熱門既時事文章<br />\n特別係commentary<br />\n同埋記吓唔同既concept words<br />\n咁就多好多</blockquote><br />\n咩concept words</blockquote><br />\n例如 compensated dating / elitism 等等"},{"pid":"9cd3cc9a289d753a4f04dec6f9e804ae13d2b285","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8da16d34a16870466be9707456f453309d4d814","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27b31e2a0919dd88981bfc62a48ad97ba5ad6bd","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1399a1a5e3987df135012a6103aeb300973189","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad69e5773e9fd07773ec43a280e36395656c7b7","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c320b9c90bb2892470d8e7c3c7cb647f6c342ea4","tid":376931,"uid":11058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b078583a860f7cdce56cb24555e84be46eec840f","tid":376931,"uid":